Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.17,0:00:10.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪(小町)ねえ\N(比企谷)うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.95,0:00:10.05,Default,Komachi,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.74,0:00:12.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(小町)なんかあった？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.94,0:00:12.03,Default,Komachi,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.86,0:00:16.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんもねえよ\Nむしろアレだな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:15.76,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:20.13,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,In fact, I'd say there's actually too much nothing happening in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.84,0:00:19.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆に俺の人生\Nなんもなさすぎるまである
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.84,0:00:22.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人間万事塞翁が馬っつーけど
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.13,0:00:22.45,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,They say "inscrutable are the ways of Heaven,"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.18,0:00:26.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,多少なんかあったほうが\Nうまくいくのかもしれんな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.45,0:00:25.54,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,but maybe things go better when there's a little something going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.10,0:00:29.44,Default,Komachi,0,0,0,,What happened, Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.19,0:00:29.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしたの？ お兄ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.17,0:00:31.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや まあ なんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.44,0:00:32.08,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Oh, well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:34.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんもねえってことだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.08,0:00:34.01,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,That just means nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.49,0:00:39.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ 知ってる？\Nなに 豆しば？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.69,0:00:38.05,Default,Komachi,0,0,0,,Hey, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.05,0:00:39.31,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,What's this, Mameshiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.31,0:00:42.35,Default,Komachi,0,0,0,,You always say all that hopeless stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.55,0:00:42.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お兄ちゃんは普段から\Nどうしようもないこと言うけど➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.35,0:00:45.89,Default,Komachi,0,0,0,,but when you're down, you sound even more hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:46.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,調子悪いときは さらに\Nどうしようもないこと言うんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.19,0:00:48.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ そう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.69,0:00:47.65,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Oh, do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.52,0:00:50.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのさ\Nうん？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.97,0:00:50.24,Default,Komachi,0,0,0,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:53.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結衣さんと雪乃さんと\Nなにかあった？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.94,0:00:53.66,Default,Komachi,0,0,0,,Did something happen with Yui-san and Yukino-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.83,0:00:57.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつらが\Nなにか言ってたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.59,0:00:57.72,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Did they say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:01:00.49,Default,Komachi,0,0,0,,It's just what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.90,0:01:00.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ小町が\Nそう思っただけだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.49,0:01:01.56,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.67,0:01:02.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.54,0:01:05.07,Default,Komachi,0,0,0,,So? What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.67,0:01:05.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そいでさ なにやらかしたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.02,0:01:08.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が なんかやったっつー前提が\Nおかしいだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.07,0:01:07.79,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Why do you just assume that I did something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:12.32,Default,Komachi,0,0,0,,Well, you might have done something without realizing it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.01,0:01:10.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お兄ちゃんに自覚はなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.01,0:01:13.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なにかやってる可能性は\Nあるでしょうに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.32,0:01:15.73,Default,Komachi,0,0,0,,Oh, fine. Tell me every detail, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.10,0:01:15.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仕方ない 一つ一つ 話してみそ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.52,0:01:18.43,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,What do I say to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.52,0:01:18.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう言われてもな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:25.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱ なんもねえな\N≪(小町)またまた～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:23.68,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Nope, nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:25.39,Default,Komachi,0,0,0,,What, again with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:27.85,Default,Komachi,0,0,0,,So what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:27.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,で なにがあったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.85,0:01:31.11,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,You're getting pushy. Give it a rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.85,0:01:31.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しつけえよ\Nいい加減にしろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.52,0:01:34.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なに その言い方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.86,0:01:34.49,Default,Komachi,0,0,0,,Why'd you have to say it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:36.90,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,What did I say that wasn't normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.67,0:01:36.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別に普通のこと言っただけだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.84,0:01:39.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実際 しつこかったし\Nウザかった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:40.03,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,You were being pushy, and it was annoying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.84,0:01:43.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふ～ん そう➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:43.20,Default,Komachi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.86,0:01:46.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ もういい 聞かない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.43,0:01:46.49,Default,Komachi,0,0,0,,Fine. I won't ask anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:48.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうしてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.49,0:01:47.96,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Good. Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:53.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(小町の足音)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.35,0:01:56.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,小町 先 行くから\N鍵かけといて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.77,0:01:55.97,Default,Komachi,0,0,0,,I'm leaving now. Remember to lock the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.19,0:01:58.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:57.24,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.54,0:02:00.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(強くドアが閉まる)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:04.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪(小町)やっぱ\Nなんかあったんじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.61,0:02:03.83,Default,Komachi,0,0,0,,Something totally happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:06.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(小町が小走りする足音)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.22,0:02:18.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:16.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おはよ～\N≪(女生徒)おはよ～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.63,0:02:14.75,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:16.11,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.76,0:02:19.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<変わらないことを>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:23.39,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,A world that wants nothing to change... that wants stagnation, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.76,0:02:23.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<停滞することを望んだ世界 か…>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.39,0:02:25.62,Default,Saika,0,0,0,,Morning, Hachiman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:27.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(戸塚)おはよう 八幡 エヘヘッ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:29.49,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Oh, morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.57,0:02:30.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ おはよう\Nあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:33.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした？\Nああ いや
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.24,0:02:32.05,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.05,0:02:33.19,Default,Saika,0,0,0,,Ah, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:35.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんか普通に挨拶だなって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:35.63,Default,Saika,0,0,0,,I just thought that was a pretty normal greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.43,0:02:38.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ まあ そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:38.01,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Oh... Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.08,0:02:40.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,普通だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:39.62,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,That's normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:47.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(結衣)あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:07.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,苦え…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:07.41,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Bitter...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.75,0:03:23.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ため息)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:27.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(結衣の笑い声)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.78,0:03:32.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんでさ 駅前のｸﾚｰﾌﾟ屋さんがね\N超おいしいんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.88,0:03:32.73,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,Yeah, and that crêpe place by the station is so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.47,0:03:35.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪(雪乃)そう\Nゆきのん 一緒に行こう！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:33.35,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:35.92,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,Let's go there together, Yukinon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:37.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チョコバナナが…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.92,0:03:37.54,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,The choco-banana is be—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:46.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:53.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来たのね\Nああ まあな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:51.07,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,So you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.07,0:03:52.90,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:08.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あッ そういえば\Nみんな 普通だったね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.88,0:04:08.60,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, everyone seemed pretty normal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:13.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その えっと みんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:13.69,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,I mean, uh... Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:15.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだな\Nあッ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:15.35,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.41,0:04:18.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見てる限りじゃ\Nなんともなさそうだったな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:18.65,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Nothing seemed out of place as far as I could see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.58,0:04:22.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう ならいいのだけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.85,0:04:22.40,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,Really? That's good, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:27.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや～ 結構\Nヒヤヒヤしてたんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:27.38,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,Man, I was pretty nervous,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:30.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が心配することじゃなかったな\Nみたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.38,0:04:31.09,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,but now it's like I shouldn't have been worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:35.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな 全然 普通で…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:34.92,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,They're all... totally normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:40.17,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're thinking anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:40.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なに考えてるのか\Nよく分かんなくなっちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:44.93,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,We could never tell what he was thinking in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.23,0:04:45.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,元々 なにを考えているかなんて\N私達には分からないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.14,0:04:47.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お互いを知っていたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.48,0:04:47.44,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,Even if we know each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.42,0:04:50.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,理解できるかは\Nまた別の問題だもの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:49.93,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,understanding each other is another matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.09,0:04:52.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ あんまり気にしてもアレだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:52.87,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Well, no point in worrying about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:55.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺達も普通にしてやるのが\N一番じゃねえの？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:55.69,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Isn't it best for us to just be normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:05:01.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私達も普通に… うん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:05:00.58,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,We should be normal, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:01.59,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:04.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,普通… ね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:03.19,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,Normal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:09.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう それが\Nあなたにとっての普通なのね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:09.24,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,So that's what's normal for you, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:14.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,変わらないと そう言うのね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.36,0:05:14.12,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,To not change, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:18.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたは…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:17.60,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:23.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その…\Nゆきのん！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:21.88,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:23.81,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,Yukinon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:26.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あッ あの… あのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.81,0:05:26.88,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,H-Hey... You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:28.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ノック)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(平塚)邪魔するぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:29.51,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:33.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少し頼みたいことがあるんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:32.63,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,I want to ask you guys a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:36.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん？ なにかあったのかね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:36.45,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:39.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや なにも\Nそれより なんか用ですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.45,0:05:39.36,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,No, nothing. Did you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:41.86,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,Yeah. You can come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.41,0:05:41.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ 入ってきていいぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:44.61,Default,Meguri,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.93,0:05:44.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(めぐり)ちょっと\N相談したいことがあって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:46.86,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,Shiromeguri-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:46.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,城廻先輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:51.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あッ いろはちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:50.99,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,Iroha-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:53.24,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,Yui-senpai! Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.19,0:05:53.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(いろは)結衣先輩 こんにちは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:55.75,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,Yahello! It's been ages!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.42,0:05:55.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっはろー 久しぶり
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:57.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:05.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生徒会長選挙の候補者？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.69,0:06:05.26,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,You're running for student council president?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.44,0:06:07.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.58,0:06:07.01,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:11.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あッ 今 向いてなさそうとか\N思いませんでした？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:11.48,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,You just thought I don't seem cut out for that, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:13.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あッ いや 別に…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:13.11,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Uh, no, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:15.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よく言われるから\N分かるんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.11,0:06:15.80,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,I get that all the time, so I can tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:18.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,トロそうとか 鈍そうとか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:18.44,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,That I seem slow, or dumb...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:20.71,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,So, is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:20.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで なにか問題が？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:24.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一色さんは 生徒会長に\N立候補してるんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.71,0:06:24.50,Default,Megumi,0,0,0,,Isshiki-san is running for student council president,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:27.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その… なんて言うのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:27.19,Default,Megumi,0,0,0,,but, well... how to put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:29.11,Default,Megumi,0,0,0,,We want to make sure she's not elected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:29.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当選しないようにしたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:34.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あッ… えっと つまり生徒会長を\Nやりたくないってこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:35.19,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,Um... Then you don't want to be the student council president?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:36.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪(いろは)ああ はい そうです
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.19,0:06:36.54,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:38.54,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,Then why are you running?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なら なぜ立候補を？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:42.37,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't volunteer myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:42.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっと 私が自分で\N立候補したんじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:44.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝手にされてて～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:44.41,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,Someone else put me in the running.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.26,0:06:46.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<なにそれ どこのアイドル？>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:46.17,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,Wait, what is this? What idol are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:49.63,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,I guess you could say I stand out, in a bad way?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:49.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私 結構\N悪目立ちっていうんですか…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:53.11,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,{\an8}She does seem like the type that other girls would despise, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:53.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<しかし アレだな こいつ\Nホントに女子に嫌われそう>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:54.49,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,I'm the soccer team manager, \Nand I'm friends with Hayama-senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.08,0:06:55.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<中学にもいたなあ そりゃもう>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.11,0:06:55.26,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,{\an8}I knew girls like that in middle school...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:57.08,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,so I guess that's how people see me now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:59.44,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,{\an8}Girls who'd play guys like some kind of juggler.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:59.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<ジャグラーばりに\N男子を手玉に取りまくりだった>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:59.44,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,A lot of people say I'd be great in the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:02.44,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,That's rather elaborate for a prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:02.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いたずらにしても\Nずいぶん手が込んでますね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:06.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,立候補には 30人以上の推薦人が\N必要だったと思いますが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:07.03,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,I believe you need at least 30 supporters in order to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:09.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなに？ よく集めたね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:09.72,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,That much? I'm impressed they found so many.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:12.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無論 しでかした生徒は\Nこちらで指導する
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:12.45,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,I'll give the student who did it a talking-to, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.44,0:07:15.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やりたくないなら\N選挙で落ちればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:15.19,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,If you don't want to do it, just lose the vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.09,0:07:17.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,というか それしかないだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.19,0:07:16.95,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Actually, isn't that the only way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:21.08,Default,Meguri,0,0,0,,Yeah, but the thing is, Isshiki-san is the only candidate...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.09,0:07:21.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,う～ん ただ\N立候補が一色さんだけだから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:23.46,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,So it's a vote of confidence, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.13,0:07:23.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,となると 信任投票ですね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:28.44,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,It'd look really pathetic to lose in a vote of confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:28.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信任投票で落選って\N超カッコ悪いじゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:32.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あッ 応援演説をやるヤツは\N決まってるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:32.93,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Do you have someone in mind to give your campaign speech?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:35.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いえ\Nなら簡単で手っとり早い
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:33.86,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.86,0:07:35.60,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Then this'll be quick and easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:37.87,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,Uh... What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:37.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっと どういうこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.76,0:07:41.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最悪 信任投票になっても\N確実に落選できて
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:41.35,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Even if it ends up a vote of confidence, we just need to make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:45.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一色は ﾉｰﾀﾞﾒｰｼﾞで切り抜けられれば\Nいいってことなんじゃねえの？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:45.52,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,she can definitely lose without taking any damage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:47.46,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,In short, everyone just
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:48.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,要は 一色が原因で\N落選したわけじゃないってことを
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,needs to understand that it's not Isshiki's fault she lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:52.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなが分かってりゃいい\Nそんなこと できるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.89,0:07:52.36,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,Can we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:55.59,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,If people lose confidence in her because of her campaign speech,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.43,0:07:55.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,応援演説が原因で\N不信任になるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:58.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰も一色のことは\N気にしないだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.59,0:07:58.00,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,no one will give Isshiki a second thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:02.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.43,0:08:11.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ その演説ってさ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:13.52,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,So, who's going to give that speech?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.44,0:08:14.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰がやるのかな…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:18.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういうの ヤダな\Nそれは…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:17.92,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,I don't want to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:18.97,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:21.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,できるヤツがやれば\Nいいんじゃねえの？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:21.76,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,we just need someone who can do it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.76,0:08:24.39,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,I can't approve of going about it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.92,0:08:25.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのやり方を\N認めるわけにはいかないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.58,0:08:30.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,理由は？\Nそれは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:27.90,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Your reason being?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:29.40,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:32.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確実性がないからよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:32.78,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,It's too uncertain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:36.02,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,And a speech that breaks confidence in Isshiki-san
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:35.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに 不信任になるような\Nひどい演説は
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:38.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一色さんにも迷惑がかかるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:38.78,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,would cause problems for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:41.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仮に不信任になったとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:41.92,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,And even if it worked,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:44.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,再選挙なんて\Nわざわざすると思う？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.92,0:08:44.04,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,do you think they'd have a second election?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.19,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:48.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それから…\N生徒会への関心が低いのだから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.11,0:08:48.29,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,There's not much interest in the student council,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:50.74,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,so if they just announce the results without giving the numbers,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:51.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,票数を公開せず 結果だけ出しても\N誰も気にしないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,no one will care.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:54.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり\Nその気になれば いくらでも…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:54.35,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,That means if they wanted to, they could...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.19,0:08:58.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,雪ノ下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.28,0:08:57.30,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,Yukinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:09:01.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,失言でした 撤回します
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:01.31,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have said that. I take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:04.88,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,The only way is to back another candidate
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:07.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,他の候補を擁立し 選挙で勝つしか\N方法はないでしょうね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.88,0:09:07.13,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,and have them win the election.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:09.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな やる気のある人間なら
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.13,0:09:09.06,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,If there's anyone willing to do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:12.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう立候補してないと\Nおかしいだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.39,0:09:11.69,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,wouldn't they already be in the running by now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:18.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも やってくれそうな人に\N当たってみれば…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.77,0:09:15.44,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,But, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.44,0:09:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If we try asking some people who might do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:24.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すぐに結論は出なそうだな\Nまた後日にしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.36,0:09:22.70,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,Looks like this one won't be solved right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:24.58,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,Let's try another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:26.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪(めぐり)はい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:25.96,Default,Meguri,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:29.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,平塚先生\Nうん？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:28.71,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,Hiratsuka-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:33.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少しよろしいでしょうか\Nうん？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:31.84,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,Do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:37.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今のところ\N勝敗はどうなっていますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:37.72,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,What are the standings right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:38.53,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.83,0:09:39.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あッ？\N勝敗って？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:39.94,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,Standings?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:42.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰が一番 人に奉仕できるか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:42.29,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,A showdown to see who can do the most service,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.09,0:09:44.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人の悩みを\N解決できるかって勝負だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.29,0:09:44.73,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,and solve the most people's problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:46.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ？\N勝ったら なんでも
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:48.28,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,The winner can order the loser to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:49.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言うことを聞いてもらえる\Nそんなのあったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:49.61,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,We were doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:51.53,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:51.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そッ そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:55.15,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,Well, you did work together on several of those cases...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.76,0:09:55.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ 協力して\N事に当たる場合が多かったからな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:57.99,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,I think you're all coming along well. Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:58.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな\Nよくやってる感じだな うん！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:10:01.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(平塚のため息)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.42,0:10:04.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３人の相対的な評価であれば
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:04.28,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,If you want a relative assessment of the three of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.09,0:10:07.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の独断と偏見で\N下すことができるが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.28,0:10:07.31,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,I can give you one from my own biased perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.13,0:10:09.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで構いません
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:09.04,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,That would be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:13.13,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,If I'm just evaluating your results alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:13.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,単純な結果だけを\N評価するのであれば➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:15.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,比企谷が一歩勝る➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.60,0:10:15.71,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,Hikigaya's a step ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.47,0:10:18.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっとも 過程や事後の経過を\N考慮に入れると➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:18.38,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,But if I consider your methods and follow-ups,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:20.82,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,Yukinoshita's faring better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:22.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,雪ノ下のほうがよかろう\Nともあれ いずれにしても➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:22.18,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,But either way,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.09,0:10:26.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,由比ヶ浜の貢献なくしては\N成り立たないものではあるが…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd never get anywhere without Yuigahama's contributions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:28.85,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,So you're saying there is no winner yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:28.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり 勝負は まだついてないと
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:30.52,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,That's what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:30.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういうことになる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:35.68,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,Then even if our opinions are divided, it won't be a problem, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:34.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なら 私達の意見が割れても\Nなんら問題ない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:37.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ということになりますね\Nえッ どういうこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.68,0:10:37.73,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.51,0:10:41.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私と彼が 同じやり方をとる必要は\Nないということよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.73,0:10:42.68,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,I mean he and I don't have to use the same method.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:44.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ…\Nまあ そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.68,0:10:44.04,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Yeah, true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:47.16,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,No point in working together against our will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:47.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お互い 無理して合わせたって\N意味ないしな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:50.33,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,So what's the club going to do until you reach a solution?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.32,0:10:50.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで 解決するまで\N部活はどうするかね？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:52.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自由参加でよいかと
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:52.46,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,I suggest free participation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:54.09,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,I guess that's reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:55.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪(平塚)まあ 妥当なところか\Nああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.66,0:11:00.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なれ合いなんて 私もあなたも\N一番嫌うものだったのにね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:10:57.43,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,And I thought that kind
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.43,0:11:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of deception was what you and I both hated most.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:04.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪(平塚)なにかあったのかね？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:04.88,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.77,0:11:07.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なにも\Nそうか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.88,0:11:06.50,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.50,0:11:07.43,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:11.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあいい 君は優しいからな➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.94,0:11:09.18,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:11.56,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,You're such a nice kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:14.24,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,I know you've helped a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.79,0:11:14.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,救われた人間だって少なくない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.09,0:11:16.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや そういうことは…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:16.30,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:20.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は こう見えて\N結構 えこひいきするんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.84,0:11:20.74,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,Despite appearances, there are certain people I'm partial to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:22.89,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Is that acceptable for a teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.77,0:11:23.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それ 教師として\Nどうなんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:25.23,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,I believe in helping people grow through praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:27.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,褒めて伸ばす方針でね\Nとても そうは思えませんけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.23,0:11:27.24,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.42,0:11:30.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その分 叱りもするからな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:30.25,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,But I give just as much discipline, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:31.77,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,With the way you do things,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.43,0:11:34.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君のやり方では 本当に助けたい\N誰かに出会ったとき
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.77,0:11:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,when you meet someone you really want to help,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:37.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,助けることができないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:36.50,Default,Hira,0,0,0,,you won't be able to.
