Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.90,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:58.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございました
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:01.11,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Hey, there's a face I don't see often.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:12:02.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(陽乃)おや 珍しい顔だ ウッフフ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:07.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.77,0:12:10.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別に逃げることないじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.82,0:12:11.14,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,There was no need to run away, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.92,0:12:12.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,失礼だなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:12.25,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Talk about rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:20.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,比企谷君\Nはい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.01,0:12:19.56,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Hikigaya-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.56,0:12:20.01,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:22.54,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Tell me something interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.08,0:12:22.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんか面白い話して
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:26.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その超嫌そうなリアクション
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:26.15,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,That super disgusted reaction!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:28.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや～ 期待どおりだな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.15,0:12:28.76,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's everything I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.42,0:12:31.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ 雪乃ちゃんは元気？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:31.78,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Hey, how's Yukino-chan doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:34.52,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Well, same as ever, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.82,0:12:34.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ 普段と変わらずですかね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:36.65,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Yeah? Glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.59,0:12:36.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪(陽乃)そっか なら よかった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:39.73,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,And? Have there been any developments?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:39.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで\N少しは進展があったのかね？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,0:12:42.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ…\N修学旅行あったんじゃないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:40.23,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:42.50,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Didn't you have a field trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:46.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よく知ってますね\Nうちに お土産 届いたから
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:44.00,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,You know about that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.00,0:12:45.91,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,She sent souvenirs home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:48.49,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,She had them delivered?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:48.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わざわざ宅配便を…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:50.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,顔を合わせたくなかったんでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:50.75,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,She probably didn't want to see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.57,0:12:53.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なのに お土産は買っていくのか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.75,0:12:52.91,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Yet she bought souvenirs for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:55.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,律儀だな\Nああ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:54.21,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Dutiful of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:57.54,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't think that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:57.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういうのじゃないと思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:13:01.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,嫌いだけど\N嫌われたくはないのよね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.87,0:13:00.63,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,She hates us, but she doesn't want us to hate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.73,0:13:05.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも もう大きな行事もなくなるし
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:05.54,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,But there won't be any more big events at school,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:08.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとは受験に集中って感じかな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.54,0:13:08.11,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,so I guess the rest will be preparing for exams, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:11.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,退屈なんじゃない？\N別に そうでも
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.11,0:13:09.65,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Won't you be bored?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.65,0:13:11.06,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Not particularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:14.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生徒会選挙とか\Nまだ なんやかんやありますし
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.57,0:13:15.04,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,There's still the student council election and other stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.75,0:13:18.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あッ そっか\Nめぐりも ようやく引退だね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.04,0:13:16.19,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:18.77,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Meguri'll finally have to retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:20.59,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Knowing Meguri, I bet
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.78,0:13:20.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうせ めぐりのことだから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,she asked Yukino-chan to be the next president, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.74,0:13:24.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,雪乃ちゃんに 生徒会長やってくれ\Nって頼んだんじゃないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:26.95,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,No, actually, she didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.12,0:13:27.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ いや\Nそういうことはなかったですね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:29.70,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,No? How boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:31.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な～んだ つまんないの\Nじゃあ 雪乃ちゃんは
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:33.29,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,So Yukino-chan won't be student council president, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:34.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生徒会長やらないんだ\Nでしょうね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:34.37,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:37.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふ～ん\Nあの それがなにか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:38.09,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Um, is that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:41.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん？ いや\N私は やらなかったからさ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.09,0:13:41.02,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Oh, no, it's just that I wasn't president.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:45.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ… つまんないなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.18,0:13:45.47,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,How boring...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.40,0:13:52.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪(折本)あれ 比企谷？➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.54,0:13:52.51,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,Huh? Hikigaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:54.89,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,Whoa! This totally takes me back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.57,0:13:56.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うわッ 超ナツいんだけど\Nレアキャラじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:56.27,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,It's rare to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:58.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,折本…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:57.98,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Orimoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.24,0:14:01.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<中学の同級生なんて\N記憶の奥底で>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:14:00.34,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,I thought all my middle school classmates
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:05.11,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,had been discarded into the deepest corner of my memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.24,0:14:05.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<打ち捨てられてるものだとばかり\N思っていたのに>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.08,0:14:09.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<折本かおりの名前は\Nすんなりと出てきてしまった>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:09.11,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,And now Orimoto Kaori's name pops up, just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:14.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれ 比企谷って総武高なの？\Nあッ ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:13.22,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,Hey, Hikigaya, you go to Soubu High?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:14.59,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:18.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,へえ～ 頭良かったんだ\N知らなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:18.37,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,Oh, you must be smart, then! I had no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:21.64,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,You never talked to anyone, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.41,0:14:21.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,比企谷\N全然 人と話してなかったもんね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:24.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あッ… 彼女さん？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:24.75,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,Your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:25.80,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:28.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや\Nだよね 絶対ないと思った
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:28.51,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,Yeah, I thought not! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.57,0:14:32.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<なに愛想笑いしてんだ 俺は\N気持ち悪い>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.48,0:14:32.51,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,Why am I forcing myself to laugh? Creepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:35.13,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Could it be this is a friend of yours, Hikigaya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.59,0:14:34.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もしかして 比企谷君のお友達？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.91,0:14:37.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<その聞き方だと\N｢友達いたの？｣に聞こえるのは>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:36.41,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,When you say it like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.41,0:14:39.59,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,is it my imagination or does it sound like "You have a friend?" Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.91,0:14:39.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<気のせいですか そうですか>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.59,0:14:41.52,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,She was in my class in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:43.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中学の同級生です\N折本かおりです
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:43.27,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,I'm Orimoto Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:47.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふ～ん…\Nああ 私は雪ノ下陽乃ね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:49.86,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm Yukinoshita Haruno, Hikigaya-kun's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:51.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,比企谷君の… ねえ\Nうん？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:51.24,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:55.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私って 比企谷君のなんなの？\Nいや 俺に聞かれても
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:53.36,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,What am I to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.36,0:14:55.41,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Uh, don't ask me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:58.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,友達っていうのは変だよね➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:58.77,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,It'd be weird to say I'm a friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:15:01.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ お姉さんとか…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:15:01.17,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,An older sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:04.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その間をとって\N彼女っていうのはどう？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:04.20,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Why don't we take the middle ground and say I'm your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:07.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,普通に 学校の先輩ってことで\Nいいんじゃないですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:07.09,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Can't we just say you're an alumna from my high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:09.76,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Aw, you're no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:09.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つれないな～➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.89,0:15:14.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しっかし 比企谷君と同じ中学か\Nなんか面白いことなかったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:13.27,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Anyway, you went to middle school with him, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:14.84,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Got any interesting stories?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.42,0:15:16.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪(折本)ええ～？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.84,0:15:15.70,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:17.18,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Oh, like love stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:21.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,コイバナ！ お姉さん\N比企谷君のコイバナ 聞きたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:20.02,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,I wanna hear about Hikigaya-kun's love life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:25.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あッ そういえば 私\N比企谷に告られたりしたんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.55,0:15:25.99,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,Actually, Hikigaya asked me out once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.83,0:15:28.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(仲町)ウソ～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:27.56,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.43,0:15:30.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それ気になるな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:30.53,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,That makes me curious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:34.66,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,He had never even talked to me before, so it was a total shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.58,0:15:34.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪(折本)それまで全然 話したこと\Nなかったから 超ビビって
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:37.62,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,I talked to you. I e-mailed you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:37.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<話したことはある\Nメールだってした>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.76,0:15:41.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<お情けでも 哀れみでも\N交換してもらったアドレスに>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:41.37,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,To the address you gave me out of either sympathy or pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:44.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<どうでもいい理由をこじつけては\Nメールをし>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:44.33,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,I made up the dumbest reasons to e-mail you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.48,0:15:48.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<返ってくるか否かに 一喜一憂し\Nそんなことがあったことも>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.74,0:15:47.25,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,then bounced between excited and depressed, waiting to see if you'd respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:51.51,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,Orimoto has no idea that happened, \Nand probably doesn't even remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:51.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<折本は知らないし\N覚えてもいないんだろう…>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:54.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪(陽乃)へえ～\N比企谷君が告白ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:54.59,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Wow, Hikigaya-kun asked a girl out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.57,0:15:56.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ 昔のことなんで…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:56.56,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Well, it was a long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.56,0:15:59.60,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was ages ago, so it doesn't really matter, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:16:00.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だよね～\N昔のことだし 別にいいよね➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:04.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あッ そうだ 総武高なら\N葉山君って知ってる？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.74,0:16:05.12,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,Oh, hey! If you're at Soubu High, do you know Hayama-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:06.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あッ… ああ まあ一応
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.12,0:16:06.77,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Yeah, you could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:07.92,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:10.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マジ？ ほら 千佳\N葉山君 紹介してもらえるかもよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.92,0:16:10.65,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,Hear that, Chika? He could introduce you to Hayama-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:12.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ～？ 私はいいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:13.19,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,Oh, that's not necessary...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:14.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 知り合いじゃないし
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.19,0:16:14.82,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Well, he's not a friend or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:18.19,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, I can't see you having any connection with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.89,0:16:17.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ～ だよね 接点なさそう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:20.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハ…\N≪(陽乃)ふ～ん 面白そう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.19,0:16:20.45,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Hmm... This sounds fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.42,0:16:23.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,は～い お姉さん 紹介しちゃうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:23.46,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Okay! I'll introduce you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:25.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:24.58,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:27.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(呼び出し中)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:29.80,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Hey, Hayato? Can you come out right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:30.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ 隼人 今すぐ来れる？\Nていうか 来て➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:31.05,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,In fact, just come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.41,0:16:33.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,場所は駅近のﾄﾞｰﾅﾂｼｮｯﾌﾟ\Nあんた 何してんすか…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:33.47,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,We're in the donut place by the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:33.47,Default - Top,Hachi,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:36.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウッフフ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.37,0:16:39.47,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,Bye, Hayama-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:40.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,葉山君 またね～\Nメールするね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:40.72,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,We'll e-mail you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:42.97,Default,Kaori,0,0,0,,Oh my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:45.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪(折本)ヤバイ！\N≪(仲町)カッコよかった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.97,0:16:44.61,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,He's so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:48.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(葉山)どうして こんなまねを？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.74,0:16:48.11,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,Why'd you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:51.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だって面白そうだし\Nまた それか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:50.51,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Well, it seemed like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.51,0:16:51.61,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,That again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:55.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,で なぜ彼まで ここに？\N関係なさそうだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:54.35,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,And why is he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't have anything to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.42,0:16:57.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪(陽乃)そんなことないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.62,0:16:57.37,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:17:01.37,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,That girl with the perm is the girl Hikigaya-kun used to like!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.42,0:17:01.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのパーマの子ね 比企谷君が\N昔 好きだった子なんだって➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.46,0:17:05.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,雪乃ちゃんが知ったら\Nどんな顔するかなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:05.01,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,I wonder how Yukino-chan would react if she knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:09.23,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Well, that was great for killing some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:09.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん いい感じに時間もつぶれた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.08,0:17:11.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃ 私は もう行くね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.23,0:17:11.35,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,I'm gonna take off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:14.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,比企谷君\Nつきあってくれて ありがと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:14.80,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Thanks for keeping me company, Hikigaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:15.82,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:16.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:24.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(比企谷のため息)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:29.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君は 陽乃さんに\N好かれているんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:29.11,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,Haruno-san really likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:32.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ？ アホか\Nあれは からかってるだけだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.49,0:17:32.98,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Huh? Are you nuts? She's just tormenting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.74,0:17:37.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの人は 興味のないものには\Nちょっかい出したりしないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:36.61,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,She doesn't mess with people she's not interested in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.43,0:17:41.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なにもしないんだ\N好きなものを構いすぎて殺すか➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.96,0:17:39.63,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,She doesn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.63,0:17:41.87,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,She either kills people she likes with too much attention
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:45.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,嫌いなものを\N徹底的につぶすことしかしない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:45.54,Default,Hayama,0,0,0,,or thoroughly crushes people she doesn't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:47.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そりゃ怖い
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:47.37,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,How scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:17:59.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あッ… おッ おはよう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:17:59.14,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,M-Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:01.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:00.55,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.42,0:18:08.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日ってさ 部室 行く？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.17,0:18:08.63,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,Are you coming to the club room today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.07,0:18:10.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 行かない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:10.06,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:12.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だッ だよね…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:12.36,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, I guess not...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.41,0:18:18.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの… いろはちゃんと もう少し\N話してみようってことでさ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.55,0:18:18.07,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,Listen, we decided to talk with Iroha-chan a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:21.87,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,Like, we were hoping to figure out some plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:21.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その… なにか方針 固めよう\Nみたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:27.94,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,And... It didn't feel right not to let you know, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:28.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで ヒッキーが知らないまま\Nっていうのも ちょっとアレだから
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:31.42,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Well, if it's just to listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:32.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ 話聞くだけなら
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:39.99,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,How long has it been since I faced off with Yukinoshita one-on-one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.08,0:18:38.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<雪ノ下と\N正面切って対立するなんて>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:40.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<いつ以来だろうか>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:42.01,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,It'll be the same now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:45.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<今も同じだ 今回も俺のやり方を\N雪ノ下が否定する>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.40,0:18:45.77,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,Yukinoshita will reject my methods again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:48.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,<同じなら 問題はなにもない>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:48.77,Default - Italic,Hachi,0,0,0,,If it's the same, there's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:50.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(戸が開く)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:52.42,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,Hey, you're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:52.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あッ 来てくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:55.44,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,All right, let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:56.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では 始めましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:19:00.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とりあえず いろはちゃん以外の\N候補を誰か立てて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:19:02.52,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,For starters, I think it'd be best to find a candidate other than you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:05.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決選投票で穏便に負けるのが\N一番いいと思うんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.52,0:19:05.44,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,and have you lose peacefully in the final vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:09.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうですね\Nでも すごい人に負けるほうが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:07.25,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:11.33,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,But I'd feel better if I lost to someone really amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:11.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私的には いい感じです
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:16.60,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,I came up with a campaign pledge and speech for the candidate we select.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:16.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こちらが立てる候補の公約と\N演説の内容は考えておいたから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.41,0:19:19.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前らが公約 考えるってことは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.60,0:19:19.09,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,If you guys come up with the pledge,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.06,0:19:23.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,完全な傀儡候補なんだが…\Nそれでいいのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:21.89,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,that makes them a puppet candidate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:23.09,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Is that what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:27.62,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,If that candidate wins, what happens to the student council?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.13,0:19:27.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし当選したとして そのあとの\N生徒会運営は どうするんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:31.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だッ だから それがちゃんと\Nできる人を探せばいいだけで…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:31.13,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,L-Like we said, we just have to find someone capable—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:33.61,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,That'll just make it even harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.47,0:19:35.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なおさら ハードルが上がるぞ\Nあとあとのことを考えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:36.69,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,If you think about what comes after, \Nyou'll realize there's not much of a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.24,0:19:38.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大して意味ないし\Nあんまりいい手じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:38.11,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,It's not a very good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:41.61,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,Then what point is there in doing it your way?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.25,0:19:42.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なら あなたのやり方には\Nなんの意味があるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.75,0:19:47.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今回に限って言えば\Nとりあえず回避
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.09,0:19:47.04,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,Speaking strictly of this case,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:50.04,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,she'd avoid being elected and lose the voters' confidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.74,0:19:51.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,投票で不信任になったあと\N補欠選挙については手を引いて…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:51.84,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,then decline to run in the by-election...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.78,0:19:55.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今回に限って？ いえ 違う
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.84,0:19:53.65,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,"Speaking strictly of this case"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:55.13,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,No, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:58.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたは\N前も そうやって回避したわ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:57.88,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,You avoided the problem last time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:05.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで なんか問題あったか？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:05.26,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,And? Was there a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:08.51,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,You're the one who said there's no point in something that superficial.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:08.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなうわべだけのものに\N意味なんてないと言ったのは
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.59,0:20:11.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなただったはずよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:10.47,Default,Yukino,0,0,0,,You're not changing that stance,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.41,0:20:15.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,変える気はないのね…\Nああ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:14.94,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:20.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あッ あのさ あの…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.64,0:20:18.27,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,H-Hey, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:20.03,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:24.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(比企谷がイスから立ち上がる)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:27.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そろそろ帰るわ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:27.03,Default,Hachi,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:30.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ…
