Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:21:18.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:41.87,Default - Top,Iroha,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:44.07,Default - Top,Iroha,0,0,0,,Will this be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:48.10,Default - Top,Iroha,0,0,0,,If we find someone good, it'll make things easier for me, too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:50.17,Default - Top,Hachi,0,0,0,,It'd have to be someone like Hayama, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.17,0:20:52.02,Default - Top,Iroha,0,0,0,,Not Hayama-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:53.94,Default - Top,Hachi,0,0,0,,Well, if it comes to it, I'll do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:56.02,Default - Top,Iroha,0,0,0,,I appreciate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:58.27,Default - Top,Iroha,0,0,0,,No one else will help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:21:01.59,Default - Top,Iroha,0,0,0,,You guys are the only ones I can count on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.59,0:21:02.54,Default - Top,Iroha,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:05.49,Default - Top,Iroha,0,0,0,,Well, I've got club.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:07.58,Default - Top,Iroha,0,0,0,,Thanks for your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.77,0:23:44.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの～ 大丈夫なんですかね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.09,0:23:48.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それなりの人が出てくると\N私も気が楽で いいんですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.26,0:23:52.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうなると 葉山クラスになるな\N葉山先輩はダメです
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.18,0:23:56.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ 最悪どうにかする\N助かります
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.09,0:24:01.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰も助けてくれないんですもん\Nもう先輩達しか頼れないんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.59,0:24:05.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あッ 私 部活あるので➡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.61,0:24:07.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では よろしくで～す
